thread.title: BRIEF-Genesee & Wyoming's Traffic in Dec. 2017 Was 255,199 Carloads, Decrease Of 15,344 Carloads, Compared With Dec. 2016

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Genesee & Wyoming's Traffic in Dec. 2017 Was 255,199 Carloads, Decrease Of 15,344 Carloads, Compared With Dec. 2016
text:
Jan 19 (Reuters) - Genesee & Wyoming Inc:
* GENESEE & WYOMING REPORTS TRAFFIC FOR DECEMBER 2017 * GENESEE & WYOMING INC - G&W‘S TRAFFIC IN DECEMBER 2017 WAS 255,199 CARLOADS, A DECREASE OF 15,344 CARLOADS, OR 5.7%, COMPARED WITH DECEMBER 2016
* GENESEE & WYOMING INC - G&W‘S SAME-RAILROAD TRAFFIC IN DECEMBER 2017 WAS 254,700 CARLOADS, A DECREASE OF 15,843 CARLOADS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
